            <para count="1">Perform the A/C System Performance Test in
                <hotlnk document="s16025_HL1602546.xml" xrefid="hl1602546">SECTION 5.3</hotlnk>
                <xref refid="hl1602546"/>
                and record the readings.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If further assistance is still needed, contact Technical Service with all recorded
